Class CustomerBooking

  • java.lang.Object
    • sample.CustomerBooking

  • public class CustomerBooking
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the characteristics needed for a customer booking, such as the invoice number, name, the room, date, costs, whether the booking is paid or not, and the check in status of the customer. It also contains all the required setters and getters for these properties.
    Since:
    2019-09-21
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Romanov Andre, Shafi Mushfique, Stephen Aranda
